      "updated": 1775105901858,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When we have a fresh system and when we have a fresh HDD in it, we don't directly start using\nour HDD, first thing that we do is that we partition a harddisk. C drive, D drive, E drive all\nof that, So first we create partitions in Harddisk.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When we have a fresh system and when we have a fresh HDD in it, we don't directly start using\nour HDD, first thing that we do is that we partition a harddisk. C drive, D drive, E drive all\nof that, So first we create partitions in Harddisk.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
