      "locked": false,
      "text": "vgcreate vg1 /dev/sda1 /dev/sda2 -> this will create volume group of named vg1 using mentioned partitions\nvgdisplay -> it will list vgs\nvgs -> it will also show vgs\n\nNow VG is created",
