      "originalText": "1. ElevatorSystem\nManages all elevators\n2. ElevatorController (Dispatcher)\nAssigns elevators to requests\n3. Elevator\nIndividual elevator logic\n4. Request\nExternal (floor request)\nInternal (destination selection)\n5. Floor\nHas UP/DOWN buttons\n6. User (optional abstraction)",
      "autoResize": true,
